{"tid":2210923,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺韓國既石鍋飯可以屌打中國既煲仔飯？","createTime":"2020-09-20T18:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T15:01:28.000Z","uid":343520,"like":19,"dislike":124,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"54529a3e717cb77f9216d1c697a83814a7880d77","tid":2210923,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T18:42:48.000Z","msg":"石鍋飯有醬一齊撈 一路撈一路有香味滲出<br />\n而且配料勁多變 可以用牛肉豬肉雞肉 配合泡菜又得 又可以用海鮮增加鮮味 <br />\n根本係勁聰明既人先創造到出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O9Mq3Ak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO9Mq3Ak.jpg&h=94b3b9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反觀煲仔飯 一黎中國嘢已經係劣<br />\n咩飯都係用豉油豉油 勁弱智 <br />\n完全冇用到醬料黎配合食材 味道根本唔入流<br />\n然後配料黎黎去去都係臘味 肥膩野 極唔健康<br />\n<br />\n嚟到呢到一定會有人講咩飯焦架喇 但其實石鍋飯一樣做到 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結：韓國既石鍋飯根本全方面屌打左中國既煲仔飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2747e8b4bf650ba211664c50e37879fd9c5276e3","tid":2210923,"uid":120729,"like":13,"dislike":39,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T18:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aA6ZoCC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaA6ZoCC.jpg&h=259321dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到都唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b104b2f0db2e8551f1519292f823dbd80973cc","tid":2210923,"uid":96327,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"2747e8b4bf650ba211664c50e37879fd9c5276e3","tid":2210923,"uid":120729,"like":13,"dislike":39,"score":-26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T18:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aA6ZoCC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaA6ZoCC.jpg&h=259321dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到都唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T18:44:59.000Z","msg":"你呢個又